maps: distribution of mode of data collection

mode_dis<- pvs_data|> 
  select(mode, 
         q4_1) |> 
  rename(
    district = q4_1
  ) |>
  group_by(district, mode) |>
  count(mode) |> 
  pivot_wider(
    names_from = mode, 
    values_from = n
  )




mode_dis[is.na(mode_dis)]<-0


mode_dis<- mode_dis |> 
  mutate(
    district= recode(
      district, 
      "Mzuzu City" = "Mzimba",
      "Nkhotakota" = "Nkhota kota",
    )
  ) |> 
  clean_names()


mode_dis<- mode_dis |> 
  group_by(district) |> 
summarise(face_to_face=sum(face_to_face), 
          phone=sum(phone))


mode_dis_sf<- merge(mode_dis, 
      psv_map, 
      by = "district") |> 
  st_as_sf()


mode_dis_sf<- mode_dis_sf |> 
  mutate(
    total=round(
      face_to_face+phone
    )
  )


map_face <- tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
   tm_borders()+
   tm_fill(
    col = "district"  )+
  tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_text("face_to_face",
          size = 0.4, 
          col = "red", 
          ymod = -0.3,
          xmod = 0.25) +
  tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_text("district",
          size = 0.2, 
          col = "black")+
  tm_compass( 
    type = "rose",
    position = c("right", "top"), 
    size = 2)+
   tm_layout(
    legend.show = FALSE,
    main.title = "Mode data collection: Face to Face ",
    main.title.size = 1,
    main.title.position = "center"
  )
  


map_phone <- tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_borders()+
   tm_fill(
    col = "phone"
    )+
tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_text("phone",
          size = 0.4, 
          col = "black", 
          ymod = -0.3,
          xmod = 0.2) +
  tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_text("district", 
          size = 0.25,
          col = "black")+
  tm_compass( 
    type = "rose",
    position = c("right", "bottom"), 
    size = 2)+
   tm_layout(
    legend.show = TRUE,
    main.title = "Mode data collection:Phone ",
    main.title.size = 1,
    main.title.position = "Bottom"
  )




map_combined <- tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_borders()+
   tm_fill(
    col = "total"
    )+
tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_text("total",
          size = 0.4, 
          col = "black", 
          ymod = -0.3,
          xmod = 0.2) +
  tm_shape(mode_dis_sf)+
  tm_text("district", 
          size = 0.25,
          col = "black")+
  tm_compass( 
    type = "rose",
    position = c("right", "bottom"), 
    size = 2)+
   tm_layout(
    legend.show = TRUE,
    main.title = "Mode data collection:Combined ",
    main.title.size = 1,
    main.title.position = "Bottom"
  )



map_mode<- tmap_arrange(
  map_face, 
  map_phone, 
  map_combined,
  ncol = 3, 
  nrow = 1
)

tmap_save(map_mode, 
  filename = here("maps/mode_of_data_collection_map.png"),

  dpi = 300,

)
